{"tid":398399,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"比利連：要走曼聯歐霸冠軍路","createTime":"2017-09-13T07:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T09:28:09.000Z","uid":57237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26aba8a1b3becbbb68a7aa624ad49ac83a26c777","tid":398399,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:22:32.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Fiapx9xV0uLnJffjTeDtIpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=7f60f75f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴悍將比利連放言，球隊應該仿傚曼聯在歐霸盃的舊路，奪冠後重返歐聯。<br />\n<br />\n上季失落英超前4的阿仙奴，將於周四歐霸盃分組賽主場對科隆，20年連續躋身歐聯的紀錄斷纜，究竟兵工廠在今季聯賽和歐霸盃的道路該如何走呢？西班牙外援比利連（Hector Bellerin）向領隊雲加給予忠告：「歐霸盃對我們是一項非常特別的賽事。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們知道有機會捧盃，從而重返下季的歐聯，這是我們的目標之一。」比利連分析道：「與其一邊爭前4，一邊爭錦標，不如直接以歐霸盃冠軍身份出戰歐聯，無論歐霸盃對手是誰，己隊也會全力以赴。」<br />\n<br />\n年僅22歲的比利連4年前入「廠」，兩次奪得足總盃，夏天曾被巴塞隆拿斟介，最終決定留效。"},{"pid":"c9665bc5e4dc5420621ad11aec643b23976dccac","tid":398399,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:28:14.000Z","msg":"22碎就回晒塘"},{"pid":"8a654545c9ca466923112ba9ac8357963b76107d","tid":398399,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"打咁耐都仲KEEP到初加盟時水準"},{"pid":"f2bf9ba87a6e5018b8f9ba9d494df1028e30a5f6","tid":398399,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:32:04.000Z","msg":"陰公<br />\n岩岩開季就知今年都係無前4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f362b0db42f0043f8798a0bd760ea8bd8e01a07b","tid":398399,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:34:28.000Z","msg":"由佢整果個核突鞭子頭就開始變廢"},{"pid":"dd4b219222717bafa85c90a6c3f1839a84ec435f","tid":398399,"uid":48142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:54:33.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴悍將"},{"p